  <description><![CDATA[<p>Crikvenica is one of the most stunning resorts on the Kvarner Riviera and only 33km away from Rijeka with a bustling tree lined promenade and boasts around 8km of sandy and pebble beaches. With its gentle Mediterranean climate and surrounded by the most beautiful islands makes it an ideal spot for a relaxing holiday. This resort has thrived on fishing and tourism for over 100 years has an array of shops, bars, street cafes and restaurants especially for the fish lovers.</p>
<p>Stroll by the beautiful harbour or take a half or full day trip to explore the highlights of the spectacular Adriatic Sea. On your holiday in Crikvenica, you can visit the cultural events including concerts, folk performances and the traditional festivals including the ‘Crikvenica Days’ in August or the Fishermen’s week in September or just sit by the pineta enjoying an aperitif or soaking in the local atmosphere.</p>]]></description>
